      • finalizeAction

        void finalizeAction(Reference reference)
        This method is invoked after the Resources tool does its part of the action in case the registrant needs to participate in the action at that point. Will not be invoked after cancelAction(Reference reference) is invoked.

      • cancelAction

        void cancelAction(Reference reference)
        This method is invoked if the Resources tool cancels the action after invoking the initializeAction(Reference reference) method in case the registrant needs to clean up a canceled action at that point. Will not be invoked after finalizeAction(Reference reference) is invoked.
        Parameters:
        reference - A reference to the entity with respect to which the action is taken
